Package: TRexDAD
Title: Data-driven Pipeline for Tile Region Exchange Assembly Design
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Yunyi Cheng
Maintainer: Yunyi Cheng <yunyi.cheng@outlook.com>
Description: 
    A pipeline for the design of mutagenizing oligonucleotides required
    for Tile Region Exchange Mutagenesis (T-Rex), which is a crucial step for 
    deep mutation scanning (DMS), 
    by harnessing data-optimized assembly design (DAD).
